Textris You're about to experience a text-based version of Tetris. In this version, The player controlls  Each block is represented by a letter the block type will look like the letter.

The player will lay down blocks in the following sequence:  J, L, J, square and line

the player will can move the blocks by providing commands in each turn:

'left': Move block left or the player can type l
'right': Move block right or the player can type r
'down': Move block down faster or the player can type d
'down2': Move block down to "Hard-Drop"  Or the player can type dd
'rotate': Rotate block clockwise or the player can type a

Let's begin and see how many lines can be cleared before reaching the top!"
